quran[11]{c,v,t,f}:
  92,19,"Soni pangali kwa jwalakwe jwalijose jwaŵantendele yaukoto yaikuŵa ili nkuusyidwa."
  92,20,"Ikaŵeje (jukutola) pakusachilila Ngope ja M’mbujeegwe (Allah) Jwapenani kusyene (kuti jukajione ku Akhera)."
  92,21,"Ni juchija kusengwa."
  96,7,"Ligongo lyakuliona kusichila."
  96,8,"Chisimu kwa Ambuje ŵenu pe (Allah) ni kwakuujila."
  96,9,"Ana mum'bweni ajula jwaakuŵa nkunkaanya,"
  97,4,"Achimalaika akasatulukaga pamo ni Nsimu (Jibulilu) mu Chele (Chilochi) kwa lisosa lya M’mbuje gwao, kwisa kulondesya chindu chilichose (pakuchiŵika mu mpango wakwe). ",1:[“Mu chele (chilochi) chikasaŵichidwaga m’mangwakwe chindu chilichose chalunda lwakusokoka.” {44:4} Ichindu yalunda lwakusokoka yakwe mpela: kupagwa kwa ŵandu kwisa soni iwumbe yakulekanganalekangana, kuwa kwao, kupedwa malisiki, kupedwa makungu ni ine yosope yakwapata achiiwumbe mu chaka chosope chachikwika, mpela muŵapanjiile Allah kalakala.]
  97,5,"Ntunjelele-tunjelelepe! Chele Chilocho, mpaka kumasikusiku. ",1:[Akusimulila Ȃishah رضي الله عنهم yanti: Ntenga jwa Allah ﷺ jwatite: “N’jisosejesoseje Lailatul Qadr mu ilo ya chiŵalanjilo changakomboleka gaŵa ni 2 ni ngasigala kakusigala (mpela ilo ya 21, 23, 25, 27 ni 29), mu ilo likumi yambesi yamwesi wa Ramadhan.” (Swahîh Al-Bukhârî, Hadith No. 1913.]
  98,1,"Ŵandu achimakafili kutandila achinsyene chitabu (Ayuda ni Akilisito) kwisa soni ŵakuwanganya (Allah ni isanamu), nganaŵa alekangene (ni ukafili wao) kwikanila ndema ja chayichilile chilosyo chakuonechela palangulangu."
  98,2,"(Jwali) Ntenga (Muhammadi ﷺ) jwakuumila kwa Allah jwaakusooma (Qur’an jajili mu) ikalakala yakuswejesyedwa."
  98,3,"Mwalakwemo mwana malamusi gagoloka."